conds = [((data['metaschoepite']>0) & (data['totAcid']>1.0e-9)),
              ((data['metaschoepite']==0) & (data['totAcid']>1.0e-9)),
              ((data['metaschoepite']>0) & (data['totAcid']<=1.0e-9)),
              ((data['metaschoepite']==0) & (data['totAcid']<=1.0e-9)),
]
groups = ['group1','group2','group3','group4']

data['group'] =np.select(conds, groups)

def draw1to1plots(ax,df,yVar,xVar,scale='log'):
    
    colors= ['r','k','c','g']
    markers = ['o','^','D','s']
    for i,group in enumerate(df['group'].unique()):
        df2 =df[df['group']==group]
        ax.scatter(df2[xVar].values,df2[yVar].values,color=colors[i],marker = markers[i],
                   s=5,label=group + ': '+xVar + '=>' + yVar)
        ax.set_ylabel(yVar)
        ax.set_xlabel(xVar)
        #ax.legend (loc='best')
        if scale=='log':
            ax.set_yscale('log')
            ax.set_xscale('log')

xVars = [ 'totU', 'totAcid', 'totBase']
yVars = ['pH', 'U_aq', 'U_s', 'U_sc', 'U_ex', 'Kd_sc', 'Kd_ex', 'metaschoepite']
fig,ax =plt.subplots(len(yVars),len(xVars),figsize =(12,30))

for i,yVar in enumerate(yVars):
    for j,xVar in enumerate(xVars):
        df = data.loc[:,[xVar,yVar,'group']]
           
        draw1to1plots(ax[i,j],df,yVar,xVar,scale='no')
        if j==0 and i<len(yVars)-1:
            #ax[i,j].axes.get_yaxis().set_visible(False)
            ax[i,j].axes.get_xaxis().set_ticklabels([])
            #ax[i,j].set_xlabel("")
        if j>0 and i<len(yVars)-1:
            #ax[i,j].set_xlabel("")
            ax[i,j].axes.get_xaxis().set_ticklabels([])
            ax[i,j].set_ylabel("")
            ax[i,j].axes.get_yaxis().set_ticklabels([])
        if j>0 and i==len(yVars)-1:
            ax[i,j].set_ylabel("")
            ax[i,j].axes.get_yaxis().set_visible(False)
        
        
ax[len(yVars)-1,0].legend(bbox_to_anchor=(3.0, -0.3),ncol=2)       
fig.tight_layout()

def draw1to1groupplots(ax,df,yVar,xVar,group,scale='log'):
    
    ax.scatter(df[xVar].values,df[yVar].values,color='b',marker = 'o',s = 5)
    ax.set_ylabel(yVar)
    ax.set_xlabel(xVar)
    #ax.legend (loc='best')
    if scale=='log':
        ax.set_yscale('log')
        ax.set_xscale('log')
